snippet.title: 배고픈 원시인 1차 트레일러(Hungry Caveman first trailer)
snippet.description:
레인보우스튜디오 신작!
배고픈원시인 리메이크(원작은 2019년작) 1차 트레일러 영상입니다.
오늘도 즐거운 하루되세요.

스팀 주소 : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2166250/

Rainbow Studio's new production!
The Hungry Caveman Remake (originally in 2019)
This is the first trailer video.
Have a great day today.

Steam Link : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2166250/
